// =============================================================================
// Comprehensive UI Regression Test — 105+ tests across all 15 tabs
// =============================================================================
// STAMP: SC-GLM-UI-001, SC-GLM-UI-009, SC-COV-001..008
// Coverage: All 15 tabs × C1-C8 categories + Zenoh/OTel + Monitoring
// Categories: C1=Structural, C2=Health, C3=Population, C4=Temporal,
//             C5=Dispatch, C6=DarkCockpit, C7=Reasoning, C8=DualVerify
// =============================================================================

